@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_micpkv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.93 * (0.11 + wp.cos(v1 + 0.31)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.22) / (tmp + 0.02 - v0 + 0.07)) * wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.36)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.53) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.78)) + ((v0 + 0.74 - tmp + 0.18) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.55)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v1 + 0.42) + (tmp + 0.74 - v2 + 0.81)))
    v2 = 0.31
    data[tid] = v0
